longBusinessSummary: Futuris Company operates as a human capital management company in the United States. It focuses on offering executive search, staffing, and consulting services in various verticals, such as medical, accounting/finance, information technology, recruitment process outsourcing, and legal industries. Futuris Co. is based in Rockville, Maryland.
